{"tid":2436150,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"週日小丑神崇拜","createTime":"2021-03-07T01:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T20:39:07.000Z","uid":31323,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88e64668a86f9a9d9ff7813045b2985640976767","tid":2436150,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"我們在連登的神，<br />\n願人都尊神的名為膠；<br />\n願神的國降臨；<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上，<br />\n如同行在連登。<br />\n我們日用的膠幣，<br />\n求神今日賜給我們。<br />\n又求饒恕我們的假膠，<br />\n因為我們饒恕假膠的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n拯救我們脫離極權。<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。膠們。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/88/NewClownGodcopy.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/510?cb=20060825124231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F88%2FNewClownGodcopy.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F510%3Fcb%3D20060825124231&h=23fd2870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<im